# 35_JSONPath_Subset_Contract

SCOPE
- Implement only the subset used by APIGW `$input.json(path)`.

MUST SUPPORT
- Root `$`
- Dot child `$.a.b` and bracket `['a']`
- Array index `$.a[0]`
- Basic wildcards `*` where APIGW supports (confirm via goldens)

MUST NOT
- Implement full JSONPath features (filters, slices) unless goldens prove APIGW supports them.

ERRORS
- Invalid path formatting: mirror APIGW (null vs error) per goldens.
